OL,3,C'Neighbour from hell' dressed as
OL,4,CSpider-man to terrorise the elderly
OL,6,FA man who dressed up as Spider-man to
OL,7,Fterrorise his elderly neighbours has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FLiam Bain, a 34-year-old from Leyland,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to five counts of
OL,12,Fharassment towards his elderly
OL,13,Fneighbours in Parish Gardens at
OL,14,FPreston Crown Court.
OL,16,FBain had "made the lives of his
OL,17,Fneighbours a living hell" over the
OL,18,Fcourse of a decade, many of whom were
OL,19,Fin their 60s, 70s, and 80s.
