OL,3,C'Neighbour from hell' dressed as
OL,4,CSpider-man to terrorise the elderly
OL,6,FNeighbours made dozens of complaints
OL,7,Fto the police over the years for
OL,8,Fvarious incidents.
OL,10,FOn one occasion, Bain fired his jet
OL,11,Fwash at a neighbours car as she drove
OL,12,Fdown the street to make her think she
OL,13,Fhad hit something. When she got out of
OL,14,Fthe car to check, he soaked her while
OL,15,Fshouting abuse.
