OL,3,C'Neighbour from hell' dressed as
OL,4,CSpider-man to terrorise the elderly
OL,6,FOver the years, Bain also threatened
OL,7,Fto fight neighbours, spat at them as
OL,8,Fhe walked past, and shined a laser
OL,9,Fpointer at a woman while she was
OL,10,Fdriving which caused her to swerve off
OL,11,Fof the road.
OL,13,FWhen one victim complained, Bain said:
OL,14,F"You lot can't do anything about it, I
OL,15,Fwill still be here when all of you are
OL,16,Fdead."
OL,18,FBain would often wear a Spider-man
OL,19,Fmask or balaclava while threatening
OL,20,Fneighbours, which was captured on a
OL,21,FRing doorbell.
