OL,6,F"The other great concern I have is
OL,7,Fthat we are unable to even talk to any
OL,8,Fneighbours without some repercussions.
OL,10,F"Given that I am an 80-year-old man I
OL,11,Fhave a desire to live my life without
OL,12,Fadded misery from Liam Bain.
OL,14,F"My retirement has been spoiled by his
OL,15,Fbehaviour, and the lack of ability to
OL,16,Fgo about my normal daily life without
OL,17,Fthis level of intimidation is a real
OL,18,Fcause for concern."
