OL,6,FBain pleaded guilty to five counts of
OL,7,Fharassment and was jailed for 18 weeks
OL,8,Fon Monday 10 June.
OL,10,FHe was also issued a restraining order
OL,11,Fbanning him from entering the street
OL,12,For contacting his victims for the next
OL,13,Ffive years.
OL,15,FJudge Recorder Kevin Slack told him:
OL,16,F"There is, in my judgement, no other
OL,17,Fway to describe you than behaving as
OL,18,Fthe neighbour from hell.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
