OL,6,F"You have caused the residents of
OL,7,Fthese two streets untold misery
OL,8,Fwithout there being any cause for you
OL,9,Fto behave the way you have.
OL,11,F"Some of that may have been childish
OL,12,Fbehaviour but that does not do justice
OL,13,Fto the scale of misery your conduct
OL,14,Fhas caused.
OL,16,F"It is a common feature that they say
OL,17,Fthey were afraid of leaving their
OL,18,Fhomes to go and visit their
OL,19,Fneighbours, for fear of what you may
OL,20,Fdo to them.
