OL,6,F"You taunted them, saying there was
OL,7,Fnothing anyone could do about your
OL,8,Fconduct. "You told one victim you
OL,9,Fwould still be there when they were
OL,10,Fall dead.
OL,12,F"There is something the court can do
OL,13,Fand that is to make a restraining
OL,14,Forder."
